Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这份爱没有虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  请早点回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过家家的游戏  就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三千院凪不到拉斯维加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法得到黑椿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她带到那里去就是你的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  这神神怪怪的法术…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算怎样啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白樱！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫小姐！雏菊小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然不是没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是救人的话能不能用点更好的救人方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊  这到底算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您精神一如既往比什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  刚才的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说80%是鸟人的那位究竟是干什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种胡来的救人方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不如就这样被拐走了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  绫崎飒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被拐走了  姐姐会担心我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她会非常担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  一个人回去很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒先生  那孩子到底是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是鸫琉璃  是…凪大小姐的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说谎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道黑椿在拉斯维加斯警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果袭击警察局很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就只能拐走三千院凪  强迫她去拿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志藤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯独不原谅你让姐姐陷入危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  所以你是要背叛你的母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不会背叛母亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到和平解决这个问题的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭上嘴好好看着就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我机票钱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10万日元左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太贵了！5万就足够了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…5万5！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7万！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可得找便宜的航空公司去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为了这个来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西泽同学她们…今天真的去纽约了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们到了纽约后似乎会考虑搭便车什么的去拉斯维加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只笨蛋仓鼠一定以为纽约和拉斯维加斯之间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有东京和横滨之间的距离而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪个人都借着放假去旅行或者去看演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不知道悠闲地休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙是所谓的现充吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…大小姐因为没有人陪而感到寂寞了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁会寂寞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说后悔当初拒绝去看琉加小姐的演唱会之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没这回事呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没关系  就算没有人陪您  我还是一直在您身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么安慰方式！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的  就在你身边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  就算小飒不在也无所谓  我还有鸫呢  还有鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫小姐的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被绑架了  刚刚有恐吓信送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐吓信？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗  玛莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  内容非常可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}鸫琉璃在我们这里\N想让她活命的话\N就来拉斯维加斯吧\N要拿黑椿和鸫交换哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这字迹不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显是鸫小姐的字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道她利用被绑架作为借口…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出自导自演的绑架…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  鸫小姐是怎么到拉斯维加斯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是真的被绑架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这封信上看  应该是没有那个可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去鸫住的公寓看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋  真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她唯独行动力很强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是拉斯维加斯也一定能有办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我看了这封信  真的会飞去拉斯维加斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  她真是个彻彻底底的大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这压倒性的灵光一闪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:40.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（赌博默示录经典开司脸）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  鸫放电了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…她一定是这样想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做到这一步？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自导自演的绑架  多奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么纠结于黑椿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:08:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样就有去拉斯维加斯和大家见面的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  没什么深层含义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这本漫画是鸫小姐觉得最有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她相信大小姐最终一定会去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这貌似是鸫小姐最中意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我明明都说过爸爸的遗物就是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了  那么想要垃圾的话就送给她好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拉斯维加斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:51.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「そこで　微笑ってて　くれないか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:10.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小さい頃　星の数ほど夢を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:19.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私が望めばなんでも　手に入ると思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:25.18,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも欲しいものは　全部　高い所にあって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}背伸びをしても届かないから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.27,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げるのをやめた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:38.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど　あの日　君に出逢った…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:44.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微笑みがくれた　生まれてきたその意味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}知ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:54.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたがこの世界にいると
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思うだけで　生きていける
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばした　その手つかむよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:08.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何度くじけたって　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:11.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}乗り越えるよ　だから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:16.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「そこで　微笑ってて　くれないか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:51.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「你能不能在那里为我而微笑呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:10.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小时候的梦想多如繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:19.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本以为只要追寻便能到手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:25.18,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是想要的东西都在高处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使踮起脚尖也无法触及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我放弃了抬头仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:38.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是那一天　我遇到了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:44.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你那灿烂的笑容教会了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:54.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你存在于这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我只要想到这点就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我抓住你伸出的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:08.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论遭遇几度挫折　都毫不气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:11.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我们一定能渡过难关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:16.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「你能不能在那里为我而微笑呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…黑椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:02.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（原型为宝玑Marie-Antoinette Grande Complication N°1160\N玛丽皇后怀表，价值3000万美金，原版在1983年曾经失窃过）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑椿果真是怀表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前听说过一把同名的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是拿着这个的话  会招来很强的恶运的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…根据帝老爷所说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能把得到它的人的好运全部赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是招来恶运的受到诅咒的怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而当两支针交汇在数字8的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会得到不可思议的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上我认为这不是什么好东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  玛莉亚  作为尝试  你先把它拿起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎——？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  在这种地方也不会发生什么事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…虽然你说的也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放轻松地拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说有什么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这就是普通的怀表…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是运气都被吹走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚刚那是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可什么都不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The void being airtight, so we need to ventilate it. Here accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎刚才是换气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那么巧是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  快给我停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒给我脸向那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果然是因为那怀表的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然让大小姐你们拿在手上是太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}裙子都要转起圈来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与绑架犯谈判之前就由我拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  不过谈判在晚上九点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很长一段时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯恶运缠身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  保证大小姐的安全不正是我这管家的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧  黑椿就拜托你了  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  放心交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚  把黑椿给小飒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又来啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶走好运  招来恶运…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是被诅咒的怀表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有人希望得到这东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过难得来到拉斯维加斯  有什么有趣的事情可做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  米克诺斯岛之后就没跟小飒出过国了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…应该要创造一点开心的回忆才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们干脆去一下51区吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:10.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（51区：位于美国内华达州南部林肯郡，有空军基地驻扎，被认为是\N美国用来秘密开发测试新的空军飞行器的的地方，也有很多UFO的传言）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就这样定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚  快准备好车子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算它是招来恶运的怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险啊  差一点就被撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说大小姐的父亲就是因为交通事故去世的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得小心才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咦  大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  马上就迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先给玛莉亚小姐打个电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你的人生  就算充电也没戏啦）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂——！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚还是满电量的  怎么突然间就没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是故障了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子我都没办法跟其他人联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉亚小姐  大小姐  你们在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  玛莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  玛莉亚  小飒人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  刚刚还在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小飒他一下子就迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看来是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  给他打个电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拔打的电话处于电波无法到达的地区或已经关掉电源无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法接通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  迷路的话问一下路不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这多简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒…不会说英语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  钱！他身上有钱吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  小飒大危机啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去救他吧  玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？到哪里去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  不好了  完全迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这可麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西泽同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这不是西泽同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题应该我问你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒怎么会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我们是因为有紧急的事情才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  我也知道西泽同学来了美国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不是到纽约去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在约一小时之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为机体故障  飞机在拉斯维加斯降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小时之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我拿到黑椿的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怀表是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  呃…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  是我想太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  就是那么巧  我们就来到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  顺便一提  雏菊小姐正在那边阴影下休息着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  想不到我们会这么好运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到我能在这么美丽的地方与小飒二人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西泽同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不定运气真的很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西…西泽同学  您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼里面好像进脏东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用手擦的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…小飒  能帮忙看一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像有条线一样的东西在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不是吧  能帮我拿掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那请先别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒…这是到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小飒明明都无法跟人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒  你一定要没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎怎怎怎怎怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就这样  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  拿下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人白担心一场！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都在干些什么啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飒  你这家伙真过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您误会了  刚刚西泽同学的眼里进了脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏小飒  现在已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脏东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就放过你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑椿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能把得到它的人的好运全部赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是招来不幸的  受诅咒的怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}渇いた心　持て余して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:33.19,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}展開なら気分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:36.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}刹那へと誘うあなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:40.61,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戯れの中で　自由すぎるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:56.51,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}純真無垢な剣　振り翳す私を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:23:02.14,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}激しく射抜いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.99,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天使のような　微笑みで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}蜜よりも甘く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.37,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恋の罠　仕掛けてみる（感じて）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:24.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝、今スグ　罪深キ　愛ノ概念ヲ　悔イ改メヨ”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.09,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}清らかに導かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:32.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}聖なる魂　あなたを抱きしめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:27.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}Won't you show me all your secrets now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的心蜷缩在荒漠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:33.19,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩了它的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:36.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}刹那间被诱惑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:40.61,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在欺骗的爱中沉沦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:47.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,5000)\an2}Get out……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:56.51,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望挥舞纯真无邪之剑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:23:02.14,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尽情地让疼痛贯穿我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:02.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}Just say you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.43,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}You know I've got a crush on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天使般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比蜜还甜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.37,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}设下爱情的陷阱（感受吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:24.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝那罪恶的爱情观　现在立刻悔改吧”
